  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A new form of suffering awaits.</strong><br>Imagine playing a home run derby…<br>But with the same <i>infuriatingly precise</i> controls as a certain game where a man in a pot climbs mountains using only a hammer.<br>Yes, <i>that</i> one.<br>Now swing for the fences—if you can.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carries the spirit of a legendary home run derby game once known in Japan.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carefully designed difficulty — challenging yet never impossible.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For the sake of peace on your desk, we recommend a clean workspace and a wireless mouse.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the satisfying sensation of a perfectly timed hit.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A new form of suffering awaits.</strong><br>Imagine playing a home run derby…<br>But with the same <i>infuriatingly precise</i> controls as a certain game where a man in a pot climbs mountains using only a hammer.<br>Yes, <i>that</i> one.<br>Now swing for the fences—if you can.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carries the spirit of a legendary home run derby game once known in Japan.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carefully designed difficulty — challenging yet never impossible.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For the sake of peace on your desk, we recommend a clean workspace and a wireless mouse.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the satisfying sensation of a perfectly timed hit.</p></li></ul>",
